<section class="section">
  <div class="container grid grid-2">
    <div class="card"><p class="eyebrow">Potential pros</p><h2>When a warranty can make sense</h2><ul class="list-check"><li>Helps budget for covered repair surprises.</li><li>Can be useful for older appliances and systems.</li><li>One service request process may reduce contractor chaos.</li><li>May help new homeowners who just spent every dollar on closing costs.</li></ul></div>
    <div class="card"><p class="eyebrow">Potential cons</p><h2>When it becomes an expensive shrug</h2><ul class="list-x"><li>Exclusions can knock out the repair you expected.</li><li>Coverage limits may be lower than the full bill.</li><li>You may not choose the contractor.</li><li>Denied claims are possible. Fine print is undefeated.</li></ul></div>
  </div>
</section>
